data.name: AdvSettingsPage_SysprepPrepToolDeploySteps.Text
data.value:
This computer will be prepared for Sysprep when you click Next.
After both preparation and Sysprep are done, follow these steps to capture your image based on what deployment solution you use:
- If the image will be captured for local deployments, use the DISM command-line - If the image will be captured for Windows Deployment Services, create a capture image out of a Windows Setup image and perform the capture from there - If the image will be captured for FOG, initiate a capture task - If the image will be captured for another deployment solution, follow its documentation

data.name: FinishPage_Description.Text
data.value: Sysprep will be launched and will perform the final steps. This will take some time. After this is complete, use one of the buttons below to either close this wizard, or relaunch Sysprep if it failed to prepare your computer.
